casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Christopher Patrick SULLIVAN.
No. D-2971.
Supreme Court of the United States
May 15, 2017.
Christopher Patrick Sullivan, of Boston, Massachusetts, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
